kor6: 힘들고 어려운 일은 끝나고 좋은 일이 생긴다
eng7: Difficult and hard things will be gone and good things will happen.
The wealth of the family will leak.

kor6: 어려운 상황 중에 귀인의 도움으로 일을 수월하게 이룬다
eng7: You will have some difficulty, but a noble person will help you overcome it easily.

kor6: 아직은 때가 이르지 않았으나, 참고 기다리면 좋은 때가 온다
eng7: The time has not come yet, but patience will pay off.

kor6: 지금 당장은 힘들고 어려운 상황이지만, 이것을 이겨내면 큰 성공을 이룬다
eng7: You are having difficulty now, but only to enjoy great success later.

kor6: 본의 아니게 좋은 결과를 얻거나 뜻하지 않은 횡재를 한다
eng7: You will have an unintended good result or unexpected gain.

kor6: 무리하게 욕심을 부리면 낭패를 보게 되니 지나친 욕심은 삼가라
eng7: Being greedy will cause a trouble. Don’t press your luck too far.
You will have an opportunity to spread your wings.
You’re aiming at something, but it will not come true.

kor6: 하는 일이 점점 풀려 어려운 형편이 좋아진다
eng7: Things are getting better and you’ll see a sunny day.

kor6: 뜻을 펼칠 기회를 만나 원하는 바를 이룬다
eng7: You’ll have a chance to watch your dreams unfold and get what you want.
Environment is changing and it will give you a hard time.
Things are not getting better.
A miracle is coming to you.
A noble person will help you overcome hardship.
A lot of wealth will be added to your needy household.

kor6: 남의 방해로 진행하는 일을 이루지 못한다
eng7: Somebody will get in the way and you will not complete your job.

kor6: 모두 어려운 처지나 본인에게는 좋은 일이 생긴다
eng7: Everyone is having a hard time but a good thing will happen to you.
A tiny mistake will cause a big trouble.
You will not get what you want.

kor6: 미리 준비하지 않으면 큰 낭패를 본다
eng7: If you Don’t get ready in advance, you’ll see an abject failure.
Your hope and will are coming true.
After hardship comes achievement.

kor6: 뜻한 바는 있으나 잘 이루어지지 않는다
eng7: The thing you mean to get is not easily achieved.
You will have plenty and stay comfortable.

kor6: 어려운 상황에서 귀인을 만나 뜻한 바를 이룬다
eng7: You will meet a noble person in a difficult situation and achieve what you want.

kor6: 뜻한 바가 원만하게 이루어진다. 애정운, 직업운이 길하다
eng7: You will get what you want without any trouble. Your love and work have many auspicious signs.
You will accomplish greatly on what you have planned.
You will encounter a noble person who will be a big help to you.
There will be many hard and difficult things.
Tiresome things will happen to you, or you will suffer malicious gossip.
You’ll achieve what you’ve planned and get a great success.
You will get great wealth after accomplishing your work.

kor6: 귀인의 도움으로 모든 일을 순조롭게 이른다
eng7: You’ll get all the things Done sMoothly with the help of a noble person.
What you plan to Do will not progress properly.

kor6: 사소한 실수로 힘들게 이룬 성과를 잃어버린다
eng7: You will lose your accomplishment because of your minor mistake.
All things will go right.

kor6: 하는 일마다 이루지 못하니 살림살이는 어려워지고 체면도 깎인다
eng7: You will not succeed in whatever you Do. Your living will become poor and your face will be lost.
You will pass a test or be proMoted at work.

kor6: 모든 일이 뜻대로 이루어지고 재물이 들어온다
eng7: Everything will be Done as you plan and you’ll get rich.
Your wish will come true and you’ll be exalted to a high office.
Lots of wealth will be gained.
You will finally see the fruit of your effort.

kor6: 지금 하고 있는 일을 바꾸거나 주위 환경이 바뀐다
eng7: You will change the work you’re Doing or your surroundings.

kor6: 일을 하는 중간 중군에 근심과 걱정이 생긴다
eng7: Your work will be interrupted by occasional worries and concerns.

kor6: 주위 환경과 사정이 여의치 않아 일을 이루지 못한다
eng7: You will not be able to complete your work because of your surroundings.
You will get what you want easily.
Heaven will help you accomplish your plan.
You will have your long-cherished desire fulfulled.
You will get busy with nothing gained.
You will finally accomplish what you want.

kor6: 역경을 딛고 모든 일을 성공적으로 이룬다
eng7: You will overcome the hardship and get everything Done successfully.
Good news will reach you.
You will achieve less than you tried.
You will exchange ideas with a person who has a great plan.
Things will not go well.
You will hear ominous and terrible news.
You will gain a lot of wealth at a young age.
Be careful on your personal relationship.

kor6: 어려운 상황에 처해 좋지 않은 일이 생긴다
eng7: You will be in a predicament, and something bad will happen.
Nothing will go right.
What you’ve planned will come true without any trouble.

kor6: 뜻하지 않은 훼방꾼이 나타나거나 장애물을 만난다
eng7: You’ll be encountered by an unexpected disrupter or obstacles.
You will have followers.
